01:10:09,955 --> 01:10:12,957
- [click]
- Whew. lt's cold in here.

761
01:10:13,042 --> 01:10:15,126
[sobbing]

762
01:10:20,424 --> 01:10:22,550
- [click]
- [Malcolm] No, you know what?

763
01:10:22,635 --> 01:10:23,927
l never liked 'em either.

