766
01:10:30,267 --> 01:10:32,477
- [Vincent giggles]
- [knocking, door opens]

767
01:10:32,561 --> 01:10:34,979
[woman] Excuse me.
Dr. Reed is on line two.

768
01:10:35,064 --> 01:10:37,815
Vincent, will you excuse me?
l have to take this.

769
01:10:37,900 --> 01:10:40,401
- Just give me a minute, OK?
- OK.

770
01:10:43,030 --> 01:10:44,864
[door shuts]

771
01:10:51,121 --> 01:10:52,956
[soft whine]

772
01:10:59,630 --> 01:11:01,631
[Vincent panting]

773
01:11:23,028 --> 01:11:26,322
